          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Note that Question 3 is on climate. We weren’t taught that so I’m going to ignore it.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Questions",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Questions",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "I’m putting these here because its too short to be a separate page.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Describe-Statistics-Questions",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Describe Statistics Questions",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "These questions will usually be “describe” questions, where you have to describe a trend or pattern in the data given.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Use the following structure:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "G: General trend",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "A: Anomalies",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "S: Specifics (make it notable, such as greatest increase. Don’t talk about min or max because its too simple)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Try and include all three.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Comparison-Questions",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Comparison Questions",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Remember to use COMPARISON WORDS. For example, if you are asked to compare A and B, you could say:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "“A is Ax, Ay. B is Bx, By”",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "However, even if ALL of the points are valid, this will get you ONE mark because you haven’t compared them. You need to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "say something like:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "“A is Ax, wheras B is Bx. A is Ay, similarly B is By.”",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Note that you should split up the points into two paragraphs, because you also need to refer to a figure or table in the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "question.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
